<h3 class="stdHeader">Unique and flexible file storage</h3>

<p>Prefiniti's unique file storage feature makes managing files easier than ever. Your business will have its own site file storage area for company-related files. Additionally, each user at your company will also have a personal file storage area. Employees can upload project-related files to the site file storage area and associate them with an unlimited number of projects without having to upload the file multiple times to each individual project. An employee can also "send" files - no matter how big - instantaneously to an unlimited number of users by using Prefiniti's site email feature. Prefiniti eliminates unnecessary steps, which translates into more time for you and your employees to focus on increasing productivity. <br /><img src="/graphics/file_upload.jpg" width="548" height="215" /></p>